<text id="02-output-contract" title="API Authentication Output Contract" version="1.1.0" est_tokens="900" depth="essential">
  <summary>JSON Schema (draft-07) for the api-authentication artefact. Validator enforces the listed required fields + cross-field checks.</summary>

  <section title="Schema">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "$schema": "https://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#",
  "$id": "https://faion.net/schemas/api-authentication.json",
  "type": "object",
  "required": [
    "spec_id",
    "scheme",
    "audience",
    "access_token_ttl_seconds",
    "revocation_path"
  ],
  "properties": {
    "spec_id": {
      "type": "string",
      "pattern": "^AUTH-[A-Z0-9-]{2,40}$"
    },
    "scheme": {
      "type": "string",
      "enum": [
        "jwt",
        "oauth2-client-credentials",
        "api-key",
        "mtls",
        "opaque-session"
      ]
    },
    "audience": {
      "type": "string",
      "enum": [
        "b2c-browser",
        "b2c-mobile",
        "b2b-partner",
        "server-to-server",
        "iot"
      ]
    },
    "access_token_ttl_seconds": {
      "type": "integer",
      "minimum": 30,
      "maximum": 86400
    },
    "refresh_token_rotates": {
      "type": "boolean"
    },
    "revocation_path": {
      "type": "string",
      "minLength": 8
    },
    "key_rotation_cadence_days": {
      "type": "integer",
      "minimum": 1,
      "maximum": 365
    }
  }
}
]]></code>
  </section>

  <example valid="true">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "spec_id": "AUTH-PARTNER-API",
  "scheme": "oauth2-client-credentials",
  "audience": "b2b-partner",
  "access_token_ttl_seconds": 3600,
  "refresh_token_rotates": false,
  "revocation_path": "POST /oauth/revoke; client_id+client_secret; cascades to introspection cache eviction",
  "key_rotation_cadence_days": 90
}
]]></code>
  </example>

  <example valid="false">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "spec_id": "x",
  "scheme": "jwt",
  "audience": "b2c-browser",
  "access_token_ttl_seconds": 604800,
  "revocation_path": ""
}
]]></code>
    <note>spec_id pattern fails; JWT for b2c-browser without denylist; 7-day TTL beyond cap; revocation_path empty.</note>
  </example>

  <section title="Forbidden patterns">
    <list>
      <item>scheme=jwt + audience=b2c-browser without server-side denylist + ttl &lt;= 900 (jwt-not-for-b2c-session).</item>
      <item>access_token_ttl_seconds &gt; 3600 for high-revocation-SLA workloads.</item>
      <item>revocation_path empty for any scheme.</item>
      <item>scheme=api-key without key_rotation_cadence_days &lt;= 90.</item>
    </list>
  </section>

  <reference path="scripts/validate-api-authentication.py">Validator script</reference>
</text>
